user_prompt: Suppose a stribben, a vanoon, and a jentapp are applying to rent a bondle. Moreover, the stribben likely will be chosen and hence the vanoon likely won’t be. Does it follow that it’s likely that, if the stribben isn’t selected to rent the bondle, the jentapp will be?
